replies.body:
If you don't find it impactful, either you are playing seriously wrongly, or you're purchasing it on the wrong champions.  

It's still a rush item/must-buy for a number of juggernauts, say {{champion:86}} {{champion:122}} {{champion:420}} {{champion:6}}  (the class of champions who it was designed for) and some divers.  {{champion:59}} {{champion:254}} {{champion:64}} 

It just isn't a good rush item for say, an ADC or most assassins (though it is still great on the likes of {{champion:91}} and {{champion:238}} later in a build).
